2003年5月，一场正式名称为“第一号特强气旋风暴鲍勃”（{{lang|en|Very Severe Cyclonic Storm BOB 01}}）的[[热带气旋|热带气旋]]<ref>{{cite report |publisher=India Meteorological Department |accessdate=2015-05-16 |title=Best Tracks Data (1990 - 2013) |url=http://www.imd.gov.in/section/nhac/dynamic/bestpara.xls |format=XLS |archivedate=2013-09-27 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130927080227/http://www.imd.gov.in/section/nhac/dynamic/bestpara.xls |date= }}</ref>在[[斯里兰卡|斯里兰卡]]引发56年来最严重的洪涝灾害。系统于5月10日在[[孟加拉湾|孟加拉湾]]上空发展形成，是[[2003年北印度洋气旋季|2003年北印度洋气旋季]]的首场风暴。由于外界环境有利，系统在向西北方向移动的过程中稳步加强。根据北印度洋盆地[[区域专责气象中心|区域专责气象中心]][[印度气象局|印度气象局]]的纪录<ref>{{cite report | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 2011-09-11 | title = Worldwide Tropical Cyclone Centers | accessdate = 2015-05-16 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/aboutrsmc.shtml | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150321173303/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/aboutrsmc.shtml | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2015-03-21 }}</ref>，气旋于5月13日达到[[最大持续风速|持续风速]]每小时140公里的最高强度，按标准属特强气旋风暴。气旋在孟加拉湾中部上空向北飘移，因[[风切变|风切变]]增多而逐渐减弱。风暴转向东进，于5月16日退化成强烈低气压，然后蜿蜒向东北方向移动并重新增强成气旋风暴。系统从[[缅甸|缅甸]]西部登岸，于次日在陆地上空消散。

斯里兰卡5月前半个月里的天气一直很潮湿，气旋在孟加拉湾中部基本停止前进期间又给该国西南部带去倾盆大雨。风暴将大量水分引至该岛山区，产生大量降水。[[拉特納普勒|拉特納普勒]]一处气象站在5月17日的18小时里共测得366.1毫米雨量，其中1个小时里就降下99.8毫米。斯里兰卡西南部共因降雨引发的洪灾和山体滑坡导致2万4750户民宅被毁，另有3万2426套受到一定程度破坏，致使约80万人无家可归。风暴一共造成260人死亡，经济损失约1亿3500万美元{{#tag:ref|如无特别说明，损失数据均为相当货币的2003年价值。|group="注"}}。气旋还令印度的[[安达曼-尼科巴群岛|安达曼-尼科巴群岛]]及该国孟加拉湾沿岸地区降下小雨。除此以外，风暴把水分推离印度大陆，可能因此引发旷日持久的热浪，夺走1400人的生命<ref name="imd" />，缅甸也出现暴雨。

== 气象历史 ==
{{storm path|Cyclone 01B 2003 track.png}}
5月6日左右，延伸到[[孟加拉湾|孟加拉湾]]南部的[[季风槽|季风槽]]产生广阔的[[对流|雷暴活动区]]<ref name="mgp">{{cite web | author = John Wallace | publisher = Gary Padgett | title = Monthly Global Tropical Cyclone Summary May 2003 | year = 2003 | accessdate = 2015-05-16 | url = http://www.australiasevereweather.com/cyclones/2003/summ0305.htm | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141006091856/http://www.australiasevereweather.com/cyclones/2003/summ0305.htm | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2014-10-06 }}</ref>。次日这里有广阔的[[低气压|低气压区]]形成，并且基本上没有移动<ref name="mgp" /><ref name="imd">{{cite journal | journal = MAUSAM | volume = 55 | number = 3 | date = 2004-07 | title = Cyclones and depressions over north Indian Ocean during 2003 | author = N. Jayanthi | author2 = A. B. Mazumdar | author3 = S. Sunitha Devi | accessdate = 2015-05-16 | url = http://www.imdchennai.gov.in/Mausamcw/2003.pdf | format = PDF | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141006105319/http://www.imdchennai.gov.in/Mausamcw/2003.pdf | deadurl = yes | archivedate = 2014-10-06 | quote = causing the death toll to mount upto 1400 over Andhra Pradesh, Orissa, Tamil Nadu, etc., states. }}</ref>。接下来几天里，对流的强度不断变化，到5月10日时已围绕新生成的外层低气压组织起来<ref name="mgp" />。[[协调世界时|协调世界时]]5月10日凌晨3点，印度气象局{{#tag:ref|印度气象局是北印度洋的[[區域專責氣象中心|區域專責氣象中心]]<ref>{{cite report |publisher=India Meteorological Department |title=Regional Specialised Meteorological Centre (RSMC) - Tropical Cyclones, New Delhi |accessdate=2015-04-24 |format=PDF |archivedate=2012-04-12 |url=http://www.imd.gov.in/section/nhac/dynamic/rsmcobmission.pdf |author=RSMC New Delhi |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120412152908/http://www.imd.gov.in/section/nhac/dynamic/rsmcobmission.pdf |date= }}</ref>。|group="注"}}宣布[[印度尼西亚|印度尼西亚]][[班達亞齊|班達亞齊]]以西约535公里海域有低气压形成。不到9小时后，低气压进一步强化为[[熱帶氣旋風級|强低气压]]<ref name="imd" />。[[联合台风警报中心|联合台风警报中心]]也在几乎同一时间将系统归类为第一{{lang|en|B}}号热带气旋<ref name="atcr">{{cite report | author = Joint Typhoon Warning Center | publisher = United States Navy | accessdate = 2015-05-16 | title = Tropical Cyclone (TC) 1B | archivedate = 2013-02-21 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130221071623/http://www.usno.navy.mil/NOOC/nmfc-ph/RSS/jtwc/atcr/2003atcr.pdf | url = http://www.usno.navy.mil/NOOC/nmfc-ph/RSS/jtwc/atcr/2003atcr.pdf | format = PDF | date =  }}</ref>{{#tag:ref|[[联合台风警报中心|联合台风警报中心]]是[[美国海军|美国海军]]和[[美国空军|空军]]的联合工作组，会向北印度洋及其他海域发布[[热带气旋警告|热带气旋警告]]<ref>{{cite web | author = Joint Typhoon Warning Center | title = Joint Typhoon Warning Center Mission Statement | year = 2011 | accessdate = 2011-11-30 | url = https://metocph.nmci.navy.mil/jtwc/menu/JTWC_mission.html | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20090812132014/http://metocph.nmci.navy.mil/jtwc/menu/JTWC_mission.html | archivedate = 2009-08-12 | publisher = United States Navy, United States Airforce | dead-url = yes }}</ref>。|group="注"}}。

由于[[海面温度|海面温度]]高，上空有强烈的[[反气旋|反气旋]]存在<ref name="mgp" />，而且[[风切变|风切变]]也少，系统在向西北方向移动期间继续发展<ref name="atcr" />。5月11日清晨，印度气象局将强烈低气压升级成气旋风暴，表明其[[最大持续风速|持续风速]]至少达到每小时65公里{{#tag:ref|印度气象局采用3分钟平均风速衡量热带气旋的[[最大持续风速|最大持续风速]]<ref>{{cite web |title=Frequently Asked Questions on Tropical Cyclones |publisher=India Meteorological Department |accessdate=2015-05-16 |url=http://www.imd.gov.in/section/nhac/dynamic/faq/FAQP.htm |archivedate=2015-04-02 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150402105717/http://www.imd.gov.in/section/nhac/dynamic/faq/FAQP.htm }}</ref>。|group="注"}}，这天下午又进一步升级成强烈气旋风暴<ref name="imd" />。与此同时，系统因受东北方向[[高压脊|高压脊]]影响转向北上<ref name="atcr" />。气旋这时位于[[斯里兰卡|斯里兰卡]]以东约700公里洋面<ref name="Water">{{cite journal | author = Lareef Zubair | author2 = Upamala Tcnnakonc | author3 = Zcenas Yahiya | author4 = Janaki Chandimala | author5 = M.R.A. Siraj | journal = Journal of the Institute of Engineers, Sri Lanka | volume = 36 | number = 3 | title = What led to the May 2003 Floods? | pages = 51–52 | accessdate = 2015-05-16 | url = http://water.columbia.edu/files/2011/11/Zubair2003Floods.pdf | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140508215440/http://water.columbia.edu/files/2011/11/Zubair2003Floods.pdf | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2014-05-08 | format = PDF }}</ref>。风暴继续强化，于5月12日成为特强气旋风暴<ref name="imd" />。联合台风警报中心也宣布第一{{lang|en|B}}号热带气旋的强度已相当于[[萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级|飓风]]最低标准，风力时速120公里<ref name="mgp" />{{#tag:ref|联合台风警报中心用1分钟平均风速衡量热带气旋的最大持续风速<ref>{{cite web | title = Frequently Asked Questions | date = 2012-08-13 | publisher = Joint Typhoon Warning Center | accessdate = 2015-05-16 | archivedate = 2013-10-04 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131004091412/http://www.usno.navy.mil/JTWC/frequently-asked-questions-1/frequently-asked-questions/ | url = http://www.usno.navy.mil/JTWC/frequently-asked-questions-1/frequently-asked-questions | deadurl = no }}</ref>。|group="注"}}。不过在气旋季过后的重新分析中，联合台风警报中心认为风暴的最强风速只达到每小时110公里<ref name="atcr" />。{{lang|en|[[协调世界时|UTC]]}}5月13日早上6点，印度气象局估计气旋达到风力时速140公里的最高强度<ref name="ibt">{{cite report | author = Kenneth R. Knapp | author2 = Michael C. Kruk | author3 = David H. Levinson | author4 = Howard J. Diamond | author5 = Charles J. Neumann | year = 2010 | work = The International Best Track Archive for Climate Stewardship (IBTrACS): Unifying tropical cyclone best track data | title = 2003 Missing (2003129N05091) | publisher = Bulletin of the American Meteorological Society | accessdate = 2015-05-20 | url = http://atms.unca.edu/ibtracs/ibtracs_v03r04/browse-ibtracs/index.php?name=v03r04-2003129N05091 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160305084140/http://atms.unca.edu/ibtracs/ibtracs_v03r04/browse-ibtracs/index.php?name=v03r04-2003129N05091 | archivedate = 2016-03-05 | date =  }}</ref>。由于系统中没有[[风眼|眼状特征]]形成，因此风暴强度主要是通过[[德沃夏克分析法|德沃夏克分析法]]推导所得，卫星演算出的数值为4.5<ref name="imd" />。

达到最高强度后，受北面高压脊产生的东向风切变增多影响，风暴开始减弱，环流中心与最深层对流逐渐分离<ref name="mgp" /><ref name="atcr" />。5月14日清晨，印度气象局将系统降级成强烈气旋风暴<ref name="imd" />。在此期间，转向气流也有减弱，风暴在孟加拉湾中部蜿蜒向北前进。到5月14日晚，大部分对流都已消散，仅有中心附近的小范围区域内还有对流存在<ref name="mgp" />，系统强度已降至气旋风暴的最低水平。气旋转向[[罗盘方位|东南]]，[[雷暴|雷暴]]活动继续消解和衰落，再加上外界环境一直不利于系统发展，风暴于5月16日进一步弱化成强烈低气压。由于附近的高压脊向东转移，低气压的移动方向也更为稳定，起初向东移动，之后又转向东北，于5月18日从[[安达曼群岛|安达曼群岛]]西北方向洋面经过<ref name="mgp" /><ref name="ibt" />。强烈低气压这天再度增强成气旋风暴，风力时速一度提高到每小时85公里<ref name="imd" /><ref name="ibt" />。{{lang|en|UTC}}5月19日上午10点左右，风暴从[[兰里岛|兰里岛]][[皎漂|皎漂]]附近[[登陆_(气象学)|登陆]][[缅甸|缅甸]]西部<ref name="mgp" /><ref name="atcr" />，然后急剧减弱成低气压，再于5月20日进一步退化成低气压区<ref name="imd" />，并且次日就已无法再从卫星图像上辨别<ref name="mgp" />。

== 防灾措施和影响 ==

=== 斯里兰卡 ===
在孟加拉湾内移动期间，风暴自始至终都和斯里兰卡有相当远的距离，所以当地没有发布[[热带气旋警报|气旋警报]]。印度的[[印度中程天气预报中心|国家中程天气预报中心]]提前3天预计气旋可能会引发洪灾<ref name="water2">{{cite journal | author = Lareef Zubair | journal = Natural Hazards | volume = 33 | number = 3 | year = 2004 | title = May 2003 Disaster in Sri Lanka and Cyclone 01-B in the Bay of Bengal | accessdate = 2015-05-17 | archivedate = 2014-05-08 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140508215408/http://water.columbia.edu/files/2011/11/Zubair2004Disaster.pdf | deadurl = no | url = http://water.columbia.edu/files/2011/11/Zubair2004Disaster.pdf | format = PDF }}</ref>。但是，斯里兰卡政府直到5月17日才首度发布洪水警报，洪灾也是在这天开始。许多居民都是从扩音器或是他人口中得知洪水即将来袭，另有一部分是从电视或广播渠道获知。5月18日，当地有约8000人疏散到学校和公共建筑充当的应急避难场所。风暴产生的降雨正与当地雨季重叠，[[卡卢河|卡卢河]]附近的气象站在5月前15天里测得的降雨量超过600毫米。<ref name="icharm">{{cite report | title = Factor Analysis of Water-related Disasters in Sri Lanka | work = The International Centre for Water Hazard and Risk Management | issn = 0386-5878 | page = 52, 57, 59-61, 67, 103, 111 | publisher = Public Works Research Institute | author = Junichi Yoshitani | author2 = Norimichi Takemoto | author3 = Tarek Merabtene | archivedate = 2013-01-05 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130105124824/http://www.icharm.pwri.go.jp/publication/pdf/pdf_0706/sri_e.pdf | deadurl = no | url = http://www.icharm.pwri.go.jp/publication/pdf/pdf_0706/sri_e.pdf | year = 2007 | accessdate = 2015-05-17 | format = PDF | date =  }}</ref>

位于孟加拉湾中部期间，风暴一度基本停止移动，其西南气流将大量水分带到斯里兰卡上空，引发严重洪灾。受地形抬升作用影响，该岛西南部山区降下倾盆大雨，其中大部分发生在5月17至18日。2003年5月，该国以冈那潘尼加拉伊兰加尼庄园降雨量最高，达899毫米。[[拉特纳普勒|拉特纳普勒]]某气象站该月记录的总降雨量为718毫米，<ref name="Water" />其中366毫米是在5月17日的18个小时里所降，该站测得的一小时内最高降雨量高达99.8毫米<ref name="icharm" />。这些数字创下1947年以来斯里兰卡的新纪录<ref name="ifrc519">{{cite report | work = International Federation of Red Cross And Red Crescent Societies | date = 2003-05-19 | title = Sri Lanka: Flooding & landslides Information Bulletin No. 2 | accessdate = 2015-05-17 | publisher = ReliefWeb | url = http://reliefweb.int/report/sri-lanka/sri-lanka-flooding-landslides-information-bulletin-no-2 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141006110314/http://reliefweb.int/report/sri-lanka/sri-lanka-flooding-landslides-information-bulletin-no-2 | archivedate = 2014-10-06 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。降水主要集中在该岛西南部，其[[雨影|雨影]]向内陆延伸，位于该国中心位置的[[马特勒|马特勒]]（{{lang|en|Matale}}）也出现小雨<ref name="Water" />。卡卢河溢出后，拉特纳普勒市的洪水达到3米深，大部分民房的一楼被淹，并持续了约3天之久。河岸出现山体滑坡，形成天然水坝，冲垮了一座桥梁。金河（{{lang|en|Gin River}}）沿线被2米深的水淹没，多条道路受到影响，导致人员撤离工作复杂化。<ref name="icharm" />[[汉班托特区|汉班托特区]]在洪水来袭前正遭受旷日持久的干旱，令洪水灾情更趋严重<ref name="ifrc519b">{{cite report | work = International Federation of Red Cross And Red Crescent Societies | date = 2003-05-19 | title = Sri Lanka: Flooding & landslides Information Bulletin No. 1 | accessdate = 2015-05-17 | publisher = ReliefWeb | url = http://reliefweb.int/report/sri-lanka/sri-lanka-flooding-landslides-information-bulletin-no-1 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141006070624/http://reliefweb.int/report/sri-lanka/sri-lanka-flooding-landslides-information-bulletin-no-1 | archivedate = 2014-10-06 }}</ref>。除西南部洪水灾情严重外，风暴对斯里兰卡中部和中北部影响很小，首都[[科伦坡|科伦坡]]也没有出现严重洪灾<ref name="afp518">{{cite news | agency = Agence France-Presse | author = Amal Jayasinghe | title = India sends navy ship to help as Sri Lanka flood toll near 150 | date = 2003-05-18 | accessdate = 2015-05-17 | publisher = ReliefWeb | url = http://reliefweb.int/report/sri-lanka/india-sends-navy-ship-help-sri-lanka-flood-toll-near-150 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141006110038/http://reliefweb.int/report/sri-lanka/india-sends-navy-ship-help-sri-lanka-flood-toll-near-150 | archivedate = 2014-10-06 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。

由于此前的天气就很潮湿，土壤中的含水量已经饱和<ref name="icharm" />，因此气旋产生的降水引起严重洪灾和山体滑坡，其中又以[[拉特纳普勒区|拉特纳普勒区]]和[[努沃勒埃利耶区|努沃勒埃利耶区]]灾情严重<ref>{{cite report |publisher=World Meteorological Organization |accessdate=2014-04-21 |page=11 |title=WMO Statement on the Status of the Global Climate in 2003 |year=2004 |url=http://www.wmo.int/pages/prog/wcp/wcdmp/statement/documents/966_E.pdf |format=PDF |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120508011220/http://www.wmo.int/pages/prog/wcp/wcdmp/statement/documents/966_E.pdf |deadurl=yes |archivedate=2012-05-08 |date= }}</ref><ref name="dart">{{cite web | title = 2003 Flood Archive | publisher = Dartmouth Flood Observatory | accessdate = 2015-05-17 | url = http://www.dartmouth.edu/~floods/Archives/2003sum.htm | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141006072938/http://www.dartmouth.edu/~floods/Archives/2003sum.htm | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2014-10-06 }}</ref>。巴图戈达（{{lang|en|Batugoda}}）有81人因山体滑坡丧生<ref name="ocha1">{{cite report | work = United Nations Office for the Coordination of Humanitarian Affairs | date = 2003-05-18 | title = Sri Lanka - Floods OCHA Situation Report No. 1 | publisher = ReliefWeb | accessdate = 2015-05-17 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141006110636/http://reliefweb.int/report/sri-lanka/sri-lanka-floods-ocha-situation-report-no-1-3 | url = http://reliefweb.int/report/sri-lanka/sri-lanka-floods-ocha-situation-report-no-1-3 | archivedate = 2014-10-06 | deadurl = no }}</ref>，拉特纳普勒也有至少125人遇难<ref>{{cite news | agency = Reuters | author = Scott McDonald | date = 2003-05-21 | title = Hundreds still missing from Sri Lanka floods | publisher = ReliefWeb | accessdate = 2015-05-17 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141006110613/http://reliefweb.int/report/sri-lanka/hundreds-still-missing-sri-lanka-floods | url = http://reliefweb.int/report/sri-lanka/hundreds-still-missing-sri-lanka-floods | archivedate = 2014-10-06 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。[[汉班托特区|汉班托特区]]、[[马特勒区|马特勒区]]、[[加勒区|加勒区]]和[[卡卢特勒区|卡卢特勒区]]的河流水位因洪水上涨，其中马特勒区的河段高水位一直持续到了5月30日<ref name="dart" />。大量道路受损，用于连接拉特纳普勒和科伦坡的公路也不例外<ref name="ifrc519" />。约100所学校被毁，另有200所受到一定程度破坏<ref name="afp523" />，还有部分卫生机构的设备失落<ref>{{cite report | work = Plan | date = 2003-05-23 | title = Floods ravage Sri Lanka | publisher = ReliefWeb | accessdate = 2015-05-17 | archivedate = 2014-10-06 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141006073618/http://reliefweb.int/report/sri-lanka/floods-ravage-sri-lanka | deadurl = no | url = http://reliefweb.int/report/sri-lanka/floods-ravage-sri-lanka }}</ref>。风暴引发的洪灾摧毁了5万3300公顷茶叶作物<ref name="dart" />，估计占到[[锡兰高地红茶|该国茶叶]]年产量的20%至30%<ref name="water2" />。洪水还对稻田造成破坏<ref name="afp518" />，受灾作物约占地区总量的3%，对水稻收成的影响不大<ref name="ifrc612">{{cite report | work = International Federation of Red Cross And Red Crescent Societies | title = Sri Lanka: Flooding and Landslides Emergency Appeal No. 13/03 Operations Update no. 3 | publisher = ReliefWeb | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141006110215/http://reliefweb.int/report/sri-lanka/sri-lanka-flooding-and-landslides-emergency-appeal-no-1303-operations-update-no-3 | archivedate = 2014-10-06 | accessdate = 2015-05-17 | date = 2003-06-12 | url = http://reliefweb.int/report/sri-lanka/sri-lanka-flooding-and-landslides-emergency-appeal-no-1303-operations-update-no-3 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。许多地区的供电和电话服务中断<ref name="ifrc519b" />，同样受到影响的还有粮食和水供应<ref name="afp520">{{cite news | agency = Agence France-Presse | date = 2003-05-20 | title = Sri Lanka banks on foreign help as flood death toll hits 242 | publisher = ReliefWeb | accessdate = 2015-05-17 | archivedate = 2014-10-06 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141006110723/http://reliefweb.int/report/sri-lanka/sri-lanka-banks-foreign-help-flood-death-toll-hits-242 | url = http://reliefweb.int/report/sri-lanka/sri-lanka-banks-foreign-help-flood-death-toll-hits-242 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。

整个斯里兰卡有至少2万4750套民宅被洪水摧毁，另有3万2426套受到一定程度破坏<ref name="afp523">{{cite news | agency = Agence France-Presse | title = Sri Lanka pours more troops to boost flood relief | accessdate = 2015-05-17 | date = 2003-05-23 | url = http://reliefweb.int/report/sri-lanka/sri-lanka-pours-more-troops-boost-flood-relief | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141006065829/http://reliefweb.int/report/sri-lanka/sri-lanka-pours-more-troops-boost-flood-relief | archivedate = 2014-10-06 | dead-url = no }}</ref>，导致约80万人流离失所<ref name="wsws">{{cite news | work = World Socialist Web Site | publisher = International Committee of the Fourth International | title = Nearly one million left homeless by Sri Lankan floods | date = 2003-05-27 | accessdate = 2015-05-17 | url = http://www.wsws.org/en/articles/2003/05/sril-m27.html | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141006153720/http://www.wsws.org/en/articles/2003/05/sril-m27.html | archivedate = 2014-10-06 }}</ref>，许多人变得一无所有<ref name="ifrc530">{{cite report | work = International Federation of Red Cross And Red Crescent Societies | title = Sri Lanka: Flooding and Landslides Emergency Appeal No. 13/03 Operations Update no. 2 | publisher = ReliefWeb | date = 2014-04-29 | accessdate = 2015-05-17 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141006110102/http://reliefweb.int/report/sri-lanka/sri-lanka-flooding-and-landslides-emergency-appeal-no-1303-operations-update-no-2 | archivedate = 2014-10-06 | url = http://reliefweb.int/report/sri-lanka/sri-lanka-flooding-and-landslides-emergency-appeal-no-1303-operations-update-no-2 }}</ref>。全国一共遭受了价值1.35亿美元的损失<ref name="unisdr">{{cite report | publisher = United Nations Office for Disaster Risk Reduction | series = WMO/ESCAP Panel on Tropical Cyclones | title = Thirty-First Session Final Report | year = 2004 | accessdate = 2014-05-03 | archivedate = 2012-08-05 | format = PDF | deadurl = no | url = http://www.unisdr.org/2005/wcdr/preparatory-process/meetings/docs/WMO-ESCAP-Tropical-Cyclones.pdf | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120805131250/http://www.unisdr.org/2005/wcdr/preparatory-process/meetings/docs/WMO-ESCAP-Tropical-Cyclones.pdf | date =  }}</ref>，其中大部分来自民房和道路所受破坏<ref name="icharm" />。岛上共有260人因气旋引发的洪灾丧生<ref name="water2" />，其中大部分发生在洪灾肆虐的该国南部沿海，特别是居民以农民为主的卡卢河沿线。建有防洪堤的地方洪水可以随已经建成的排水系统排出<ref name="icharm" />。

=== 其他地区 ===
风暴形成期间，[[安达曼-尼科巴群岛|安达曼-尼科巴群岛]]出现中等程度降水，[[玛雅邦特|玛雅邦特]]（{{lang|en|Mayabunder}}）的降雨量达到70毫米。气旋之后逐渐逼近缅甸，给[[小安达曼岛|哈特湾]]带去89毫米降水。<ref name="imd" />[[泰米尔纳德邦|泰米尔纳德邦]]的多个气象站记录下少量降雨，[[阿迪拉马帕蒂纳姆|阿迪拉马帕蒂纳姆]]的降雨量有98毫米<ref name="mgp" />。风暴边缘还给[[奥里萨邦|奥里萨邦]]沿海地区带去少量雨水，其中斯旺帕纳（{{lang|en|Swampatna}}）的降雨量达到53毫米<ref name="imd" />。随着气旋登陆缅甸，[[若开邦|若开邦]]降下倾盆大雨，标志着这年的季风季节提前开幕<ref>{{cite news | agency = Myanmar Times | title = Cyclone brings an early monsoon | author = Myo Theingi Cho | volume = 9 | number = 167 | date = 2003-06-01 | accessdate = 2014-04-29 | url = http://myanmartimes.tripod.com/cgi-bin/search.pl?id=28&view=detail&search=May%202003 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140502001958/http://myanmartimes.tripod.com/cgi-bin/search.pl?id=28&view=detail&search=May%202003 | archivedate = 2014-05-02 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。

受风暴移动速度缓慢的影响，印度东南部上空的[[对流层|大气流动]]出现变化。据印度气象局记载，这场气旋风暴可能导致沿海[[安得拉邦|安得拉邦]]受到严重的热浪冲击，并且从5月一直持续到6月上旬，夺走多达1400人的生命<ref name="imd" />，当地气温高达50[[摄氏度|°C]]<ref>{{cite web | work = International Federation of Red Cross And Red Crescent Societies | date = 2003-06-12 | title = Indian heat wave claims almost 2,000 lives | accessdate = 2015-05-17 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141014135117/http://reliefweb.int/report/bangladesh/indian-heat-wave-claims-almost-2000-lives | publisher = ReliefWeb | url = http://reliefweb.int/report/bangladesh/indian-heat-wave-claims-almost-2000-lives | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2014-10-14 }}</ref>。

== 善后 ==
[[File:May_2003_Sri_Lanka_floods.jpg|right]]位于中下部，红色中的黑色阴影，是降雨量最高的地区。]]

斯里兰卡海陆空三军和警察在洪灾过后立即展开搜救任务。海军和空军部队救出困在树上或屋顶上的居民<ref name="afp518" />，之后还得到[[印度军事|印度军方]]的援助<ref name="afp520" />。但是，供电不足及[[基础设施|基础设施]]受损给救灾工作带来困难<ref>{{cite report | work = World Vision | date = 2003-05-20 | title = Floods kill 200 in Sri Lanka | publisher = ReliefWeb | accessdate = 2015-05-17 | url = http://reliefweb.int/report/sri-lanka/floods-kill-200-sri-lanka | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141006110625/http://reliefweb.int/report/sri-lanka/floods-kill-200-sri-lanka | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2014-10-06 }}</ref>。受灾最重的拉特纳普勒没有足够的医生，当地官员不得不向邻近城镇求助<ref name="afp518" />。洪灾发生后，腹泻、病毒性感冒和伤寒的病例报告增多<ref name="wsws" />。流动卫生工作组医治的人员超过4万4000人，降低了疾病传播几率<ref name="ifrc530" />。风暴过去后，某村庄居民连续3天没有食物，许多人甚至无法获得干净的水<ref name="ifrc523">{{cite report | work = International Federation of Red Cross And Red Crescent Societies | title = Sri Lanka: Flooding and Landslides Emergency Appeal No. 13/03 Operations Update no. 1 | publisher = ReliefWeb | accessdate = 2015-05-17 | date = 2003-05-23 | archivedate = 2014-10-06 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141006110833/http://reliefweb.int/report/sri-lanka/sri-lanka-flooding-and-landslides-emergency-appeal-no-1303-operations-update-no-1 | url = http://reliefweb.int/report/sri-lanka/sri-lanka-flooding-and-landslides-emergency-appeal-no-1303-operations-update-no-1 }}</ref>。到5月19日时，受灾最重地区的洪水开始回落，工作人员得以修复公路<ref name="ifrc519" />。政府拨出600万[[斯里兰卡卢比|斯里兰卡卢比]]（相当于2003年的6万2500美元）的紧急救灾款，还向有亲人去世的家庭提供每名死者1万5000斯里兰卡卢比（相当于2003年的156美元）的丧葬费<ref name="ifrc519" />。5月22至25日，该国议会缩短议程，以便议员返回所在地区<ref>{{cite  news | agency = Agence France-Presse | date = 2003-05-20 | title = Indian military joins Sri Lanka relief effort after flood havoc | publisher = ReliefWeb | accessdate = 2015-05-17 | archivedate = 2014-10-06 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141006110152/http://reliefweb.int/report/sri-lanka/indian-military-joins-sri-lanka-relief-effort-after-flood-havoc | url = http://reliefweb.int/report/sri-lanka/indian-military-joins-sri-lanka-relief-effort-after-flood-havoc | deadurl = no }}</ref>。到2003年5月底，政府一共拨款1729万斯里兰卡卢比（相当于2003年的18万美元）用于救灾<ref name="wsws" />，其中每个家庭收到2万7000斯里兰卡卢比（相当于2003年的280美元）重建家园<ref name="ocha526" />。斯里兰卡政府还设立四人工作组来管理抗洪救灾工作<ref name="ifrc519" />。地方[[红十字会与红新月会国际联合会|红十字分会]]动用应急物资发放了1万袋食品，还部署训练有素的志愿者前往灾区提供援助<ref name="ifrc519b" />。红十字会一共发放了约2万6000条面包，862公斤糖和1775公斤大米，还有其他多种物资<ref name="ifrc530" />。截至5月20日，斯里兰卡空军已利用8架直升机空投了35吨食品<ref name="afp520" />。红十字会工作人员清理了该地区数以百计的水井，恢复清洁水源供应<ref>{{cite report | work = International Federation of Red Cross And Red Crescent Societies | date = 2003-05-28 | title = Red Cross takes lead in clean water for Sri Lanka flood victims | accessdate = 2015-05-17 | publisher = ReliefWeb | archivedate = 2014-10-06 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141006110314/http://reliefweb.int/report/sri-lanka/sri-lanka-flooding-landslides-information-bulletin-no-2 | url = http://reliefweb.int/report/sri-lanka/sri-lanka-flooding-landslides-information-bulletin-no-2 }}</ref>，清理工作于8月完成<ref name="sum" />。洪灾爆发9天后的5月16日，95%的地区已恢复供电，许多道路逐渐重建<ref name="r26">{{cite news | agency = Agence France-Presse | date = 2003-06-03 | title = Sri Lanka puts flood toll at 254, seeks foreign help | accessdate = 2015-05-17 | archivedate = 2014-10-06 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141006110004/http://reliefweb.int/report/sri-lanka/sri-lanka-puts-flood-toll-254-seeks-foreign-help | url = http://reliefweb.int/report/sri-lanka/sri-lanka-puts-flood-toll-254-seeks-foreign-help }}</ref>。大部分城镇的道路到5月26日时已恢复通行，只有[[馬塔拉_(斯里蘭卡)|馬塔拉]]例外。由于洪灾依然肆虐，马塔拉官员为减少疾病传播而关闭了多所学校<ref name="ocha526">{{cite report | work = United Nations Office for the Coordination of Humanitarian Affairs | date = 2003-05-26 | title = Sri Lanka - Floods OCHA Situation Report No. 4 | publisher = ReliefWeb | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141006110758/http://reliefweb.int/report/sri-lanka/sri-lanka-floods-ocha-situation-report-no-4 | accessdate = 2015-05-17 | url = http://reliefweb.int/report/sri-lanka/sri-lanka-floods-ocha-situation-report-no-4 | archivedate = 2014-10-06 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。洪水基本消退后，[[世界社会主义者网站|世界社会主义者网站]]指责斯里兰卡政府的灾害管理工作不够到位，森林砍伐和宝石开采都促使山体滑坡发生<ref name="wsws" />。2003年8月发布的一份红十字会报告指出，政府迅速响应，为灾民提供援助，但洪灾也表明该国在防灾减灾方面存在问题<ref name="sum" />。

5月19日，红十字会呼吁[[国际社会|国际社会]]伸出援手<ref name="ifrc519" />。红十字会还在前一天拨款5万[[瑞士法郎|瑞士法郎]]购买救灾物资，[[联合国人道主义事务协调办公室|联合国人道主义事务协调办公室]]也提供了5万美元赠款<ref name="ocha1" />。洪灾过后的几天里，[[印度政府|印度政府]]派出船只向斯里兰卡送去充气橡皮艇和医疗用品<ref name="afp518" />。18个国家的红十字分会一共向斯里兰卡提供了230万瑞士法郎现款<ref name="sum" />。[[瑞典|瑞典]]提供80万[[瑞典克朗|瑞典克朗]]用于救灾运输和物资发放<ref name="ifrc523" />。[[日本国政府|日本政府]]向斯里兰卡提供了价值1980万[[日元|日元]]的帐篷、床单及其它物品<ref>{{cite report | work = Government of Japan | date = 2003-05-21 | title = Emergency aid for flood disaster in Sri Lanka | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141006075231/http://reliefweb.int/report/sri-lanka/emergency-aid-flood-disaster-sri-lanka | archivedate = 2014-10-06 | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2015-05-17 | publisher = ReliefWeb | url = http://reliefweb.int/report/sri-lanka/emergency-aid-flood-disaster-sri-lanka }}</ref>。伊朗红十字会送来价值6万5625美元的毛毯和帐篷<ref>{{cite report | work = Iranian Red Crescent | date = 2003-05-31 | title = Red Crescent relief aids to Algeria and Sri Lanka | accessdate = 2015-05-17 | publisher = ReliefWeb | archivedate = 2015-05-17 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150517102858/http://reliefweb.int/report/algeria/red-crescent-relief-aids-algeria-and-sri-lanka | url = http://reliefweb.int/report/algeria/red-crescent-relief-aids-algeria-and-sri-lanka }}</ref>，有240户家庭从中受益<ref name="sum">{{cite report | date = 2003-08-29 | accessdate = 2015-05-17 | archivedate = 2015-04-02 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150402102345/http://reliefweb.int/sites/reliefweb.int/files/resources/7BD5806E81413B34C1256D91004B48A3-ifrc-sri-29aug.pdf | format = PDF | publisher = ReliefWeb | title = Sri Lanka Floods and Landslides - Appeal No. 13/03; Operations Update no. 4 | deadurl = no | url = http://reliefweb.int/sites/reliefweb.int/files/resources/7BD5806E81413B34C1256D91004B48A3-ifrc-sri-29aug.pdf }}</ref>。[[澳大利亚政治|澳大利亚政府]]向[[联合国儿童基金会|联合国儿童基金会]]提供约40万[[澳大利亚元|澳大利亚元]]，用于重建学校及其他公共设施<ref>{{cite report | work = Government of Australia | date = 2003-05-27 | title = Australia to help restore schools destroyed by floods in Sri Lanka | accessdate = 2015-05-17 | publisher = ReliefWeb | archivedate = 2014-10-06 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141006110302/http://reliefweb.int/report/sri-lanka/australia-help-restore-schools-destroyed-floods-sri-lanka | url = http://reliefweb.int/report/sri-lanka/australia-help-restore-schools-destroyed-floods-sri-lanka }}</ref>。[[欧盟人道主义援助办公室|欧盟人道主义援助办公室]]向斯里兰卡捐款80万欧元（相当于2003年的94万4000美元）<ref name="ocha526" />。[[世界粮食计划署|世界粮食计划署]]向约10万户家庭提供膳食，[[世界卫生组织|世界卫生组织]]则向约10万人提供了净水药片、伤寒疫苗和保健药箱<ref>{{cite book | date = 2003-05-21 | title = UN mounts system-wide response to help Sri Lanka cope with deadly monsoon | work = UN News Service | publisher = ReliefWeb | accessdate = 2015-05-17 | archivedate = 2014-10-06 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141006073144/http://reliefweb.int/report/sri-lanka/un-mounts-system-wide-response-help-sri-lanka-cope-deadly-monsoon | deadurl = no | url = http://reliefweb.int/report/sri-lanka/un-mounts-system-wide-response-help-sri-lanka-cope-deadly-monsoon }}</ref>。风暴来袭期间，斯里兰卡正处于[[斯里兰卡内战|内战]]，但交战双方已达成停火协议，[[泰米尔伊拉姆猛虎解放组织|泰米尔猛虎组织]]派出多辆卡车，向灾区运送衣物和食品<ref>{{cite news | date = 2003-05-21 | title = Tigers join Sri Lankan flood relief drive | agency = Agence France-Presse | publisher = ReliefWeb | accessdate = 2015-05-17 | archivedate = 2014-10-06 | url = http://reliefweb.int/report/sri-lanka/tigers-join-sri-lankan-flood-relief-drive | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141006075243/http://reliefweb.int/report/sri-lanka/tigers-join-sri-lankan-flood-relief-drive }}</ref>。2004年7月，[[亚洲开发银行|亚洲开发银行]]向该国提供1250万美元用于修复基础设施，斯里兰卡政府则承担了其余500万美元<ref>{{cite report | work = Asian Development Bank | date = 2004-07-09 | title = ADB grants emergency assistance for flood-affected districts in southern Sri Lanka | accessdate = 2015-05-17 | publisher = ReliefWeb | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141006110251/http://reliefweb.int/report/sri-lanka/adb-grants-emergency-assistance-flood-affected-districts-southern-sri-lanka | archivedate = 2014-10-06 | url = http://reliefweb.int/report/sri-lanka/adb-grants-emergency-assistance-flood-affected-districts-southern-sri-lanka }}</ref>。

